B.FQ=s(["Evet, her ikisi de kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131n kabul\xfcne ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r.","Hay\u0131r; feragat ve kabul tek tarafl\u0131 irade beyan\u0131yla sonu\xe7 do\u011furur, kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131n veya mahkemenin muvafakatine gerek yoktur.","Yaln\u0131zca h\xe2kimin onay\u0131yla ge\xe7erli olur.","Yaln\u0131zca noter huzurunda yap\u0131l\u0131rsa ge\xe7erlidir."],t.s)
