B.Fc=s(["Davay\u0131 durdurur ama sona erdirmez.","Kesin h\xfck\xfcm gibi sonu\xe7 do\u011furur ve davay\u0131 sona erdirir.","Yaln\u0131zca delil de\u011feri ta\u015f\u0131r.","Davan\u0131n istinafa ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar."],t.s)
